\id 2TI
\h 2 TIMOTI
\toc1 2 Timoti
\toc2 2 Timoti
\toc3 2 Timoti
\mt1 2 Timoti
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Aya, Pol, mata nẽ promis od, are Kristus Jesus bun ibodok anĩ kilei, Negur nẽ oroya bunem Kristus Jesus nẽ aposel wõ aun,
\p 
\v 2 Timoti, neu kesu oboiyou bun pas enei atotof.
\p Tamada Negur ado neda Odug Kristus Jesus neid wau ifenẽya, wau yũya ado, wau inosiya, õ bun ibodõf.
\s1 Momoiya Megeir Ifareya Nigin Wau Yaleseya Od
\p 
\v 3 Aya õ nigin, toku bõ ado gaa ado, neu kosẽ bun karĩ aul fen, aya, neu talik tar age difen gen, Negur mala bun kisi karẽ bunem, Negur aruna aledig anĩ, de afiyek.
\v 4 Ogon maru nigin karĩ aul fen, ileyõya nigin wau fatuk irok, are aya wau fatuk al fouf nigin age afef.
\v 5 Aya ogon momoiya idegẽya sã anĩ karĩ aulen, momoiya anĩ, uruwa bun ogon tubũ Lois sinã Yunis ado bun ibodon gen, aya momoi auf, are õ buneg agef ibodok.
\v 6 Anĩ nigin, Negur nẽ ege luwa anĩ kebu wo di, futu rouf nigin wederẽ fokõ afef, Negur nẽ ege luwa are imau teten anon anĩ bunem õ bun ibodok anĩ.
\v 7 Negur ada kumĩ nẽ uur to ifanadan, anĩ ere, megeir nẽ, wau laa fiya nẽ ado, ada dug kulatun fiya nẽ uur ifanadan.
\p 
\v 8 Anĩ nigin, õ neda Odug kurõ fesiya nigin õ to mama yõf, aya ĩ nigin kalabus bun abodok nigineg to mama yõf. Anĩ ere, Negur nẽ megeir bunem, õ aya ado bagu ta fen, biya od nigin darau talouf.
\v 9 Negur ĩ kel gei fada fen, fateul ibodõya bun iweignadan, are ada ereb taka age tafen anĩ bunem sã, anĩ ere, ĩ yogon wau irõya ado wau ifenẽya bunem ĩ age fen. Wau ifenẽya enei, Kristus Jesus bun tetunem fau sain gariya inoya sã mog, ifanadan.
\v 10 Anĩ ere, wau ifenẽya anĩ gama neda Isennadaya, Kristus Jesus wõ yen anĩ bunem yaoren, ĩ laa anĩ narĩ felen, agef fen, biya od bunem, mata ado faimud ibodkeleya anĩ yaor fen.
\v 11 Biya od enei nigin aya soosi tamo, aposel ado ifelnẽya tamo igirnan.
\v 12 Age fiya nigin, aya darau enei alef, anĩ ere, aya to mama fiyaf, ere nigin, aya aib nigin momoi aun are aya keleĩ, Odug nẽ naa anĩ nigin, ereb aya ĩ kulatun fouf nigin afenen are, ĩ lo fiya kisi feleya are aya keleĩ.
\p 
\v 13 Ereb aya bun tamal karĩ won, ifelnẽya biya anĩ, Kristus Jesus bun momoiya waũ laa fiya ado, el wo dõ fen, urou.
\v 14 Awa Uur Fateul ada namedan ibodok anĩ nẽ megeir bunem, ereb ereb biya ifonon anĩ kulatun wo.
\p 
\v 15 Õ keleĩ, Asia provins bun ganan ditornan, idi atun Figelus Hermogenes adog.
\p 
\v 16 Odug, Onesiforus nẽ ibor bun wau yũya ifelnẽdiyouf nigin aya orouf, ere nigin, ĩ sain musei wau filolõ fiya bunem el fiyadig, aya kokolin difiyan nigin to mama fen.
\v 17 Ĩ Rom taun ibodon sain, aya nigin fatuk bagai imirnaf ile, dum fotou fiyan.
\v 18 Odug nẽ wau yũya, Odug nẽ naa anĩ bun, Odug ĩ ifenẽf nigin aya orouf! Õ keleĩ bagai, ĩ naig fe naab musei bun Efesus taun oun isennan.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Anĩ nigin, õ, neu kesu, Kristus Jesus nẽ wau ifenẽya bun megeir uno.
\v 2 Musei meleid bun aya wogõ au di, karĩ won anĩ, karĩya biya tamo anidi ufelnẽdiyouf, ago di, idi bagam tunĩ ifelnẽdiya kisi feleyauf.
\v 3 Kristus Jesus nẽ kusĩ tamo biya gen, õ amã geid darau karĩ taul fen, tafarauf.
\v 4 Kusĩ tamo ĩ tamo ege neid tobonuneid to kababal fef, ĩ yogon mudur ado anĩ wau al fouf nigin orof.
\v 5 Age fiya gen, gudu reya tamo ĩ gudu ref, ĩ gudu reya nẽ suma to dõ fouf are, ĩ uyu irouya nẽ teter to yalouf.
\v 6 Kabĩ tamo kabĩ totol yaledig ĩ, ketem kaũ yalouf.
\v 7 Aya orok anĩ kisi wo, Odug enei ganan nigin kisi fokõ fonõf.
\p 
\v 8 Jesus Kristus laa bunem kel fã yen ĩ, Dawid nẽ ibor bun tamal anĩ karĩ walauf. Enei are neu biya od,
\v 9 enei nigin aya darau ale fen, mosor tamo gen kokolin difiyan. Ani ere, Negur nẽ od kokolin fiya sã.
\v 10 Anĩ nigin, aya igirnẽdin anidi nigin, ereb ereb ganan bun feseya sã afaredig, are idig isennẽya Kristus Jesus bun ibodok anĩ, fula fiya medeĩya ibodkeleya ado dalouf nigin age afedig.
\p 
\v 11 Od enei momoi bagai:
\q1 Ada ĩ weim gare taun ouf are,
\q2 adag ĩ weim mata tabodõf.
\q1 
\v 12 Ada feseya sã tafarauf are,
\q2 adag ĩ weim lo fiya nẽ mudur tabodõf.
\q1 Ada ĩ nigin wa tafouf are,
\q2 ĩg ada nigin wa fouf.
\q1 
\v 13 Ada to dõ tafoufeg,
\q2 ĩ de agef dõ fouf,
\q2 ere nigin, ĩ yogo nigin wa fiya kisi feleya sã.
\s1 Kabĩ Tamo Negurem Ile Fen, De Yen
\p 
\v 14 Idi ereb ereb enei nigin toku wedereid fokõ wouf. Negur mala bun, od luwa irouya nigin wedereid urou, are kaũ sã, are karĩ def anidi tadũ difedidig dogol.
\v 15 Õ Negur mala bun, kabĩ tamo ile fen, de youf, are kabĩ tamo ĩ yogon kabĩ nigin to mama fouf, ĩ momoi od tutuk ifelnẽdiya nẽ kabĩ el fe irouwauf anĩ, wõ wouf nigin, kabĩ totol bagai walouf.
\v 16 Negur sã ado kaũ sã nẽ od so wiyẽf, ere nigin, idi anĩ bun dilelef are, fau gai momoiya sã bagai wowã douf.
\v 17 Idi neid ifelnẽya kaisã bagai gedi gen iyokalauf, idi atun are Himeneus Filetus ado,
\v 18 idi momoi nẽ anĩ so difiyẽ diyalelen. Idi dirõdig, mata kel fãya are mogo wõ yen, age de fen, tunĩ neid momoiya daũ difef.
\v 19 Anĩ ere, Negur nẽ gariya totol ifaref, itotoya enei bun megeir fef, “Aib idi yogon are Odug ĩ keleĩ,”\f + \fr 2:19 \ft Namba 16:5\f* ado, “Ganan idi Odug yana kurõ difesif, sesen bun tamal falei douf bagai.”
\p 
\v 20 Fõ odug taka bun, safina ereb ereb gariya fire fire nem dinon are dibodok, tunĩ gol ado silwa nem, tunĩ aa nem ado mafer nem dinon, tunĩ kabĩ odug ifenẽya nẽ ado tunĩ kabĩ nanaal ifenẽya nẽ.
\v 21 Tamo taka ĩ, sesen enei bun tamal amuyẽ anĩ kulo felef are, ĩ fau kabĩ biya ifenẽya nẽ wõ youf, ĩ fateulouf, Marau mala bun, kabĩ biya yaleya kisi feleya wõ ye fen, kabĩ biya ganan ifenẽya nẽ wõ youf nigin saika fouf.
\p 
\v 22 Oosi nẽ bouwa oroya sane so wiyẽ, ago fen, madur bagai ibodõya, momoiya, wau laa fiya ado, wau inosiya anĩ, aib idi waud karẽtut bun Odug diweignek anidi geid, dõg.
\v 23 Neneya ado wadã keleĩ nẽ luwa irouya anĩ to fedẽ wo, ere nigin, õ keleĩ, are anĩ bunem kiwai wõ yedig.
\v 24 Odug nẽ ferfer to kusĩ youf bagai, age fiya ban, ĩ tamo kayau ganan nigin imatẽya ifelnẽdiyouf, ifelnẽdiya kisi feleyauf, to seye youf bagai.
\v 25 Idi ĩ kiwai difenek anidi molol nem wedereid urouwauf, ago di, Negur idi waud falei fe di, idi momoi nigin keleĩ youf nigin wau iseya adouf.
\v 26 Anĩ bunem, idi wedereid fokõ ye fen, Satan nẽ kor bun tamal, in oroya dõ difouf nigin Satan gei fedin anidi ditor diyawauf.
\c 3
\s1 Idikeleya Naa Bun Tamo Kayau Negur Ditorõf
\p 
\v 1 Anĩ ere, enei keleĩ youf. Idikeleya naa bun, morõ odug wõ youf.
\v 2 Tamo kayau dogo nigin waud laa fouf, moni nigin waud laa fouf, yeneid dalesauf, aya aya yeya, Negur kono difouf, sineid temeid sigoreid wal difouf, disennẽdi di to de difiyẽdiyouf, fateul to dibodõf,
\v 3 wau laa fiya sã, kiwai nigin weder tu keleya sã, taka dumen wogõya, yogo nigin kulatun fiya biya sã, nirãya, tobonunã biya nigin kiwai inoya,
\v 4 ne tã kiwai ifenẽya, sibuya, kisim aya aya yeya, Negur nigin wau laa fiya ban bouwa nẽ oroya nigin wau laa fiya,
\v 5 bouwedim dogol Negur nẽ tobonunã dõ dife fen, in megeir wa difouf. Idi age fediya so weid.
\p 
\v 6 Age fediya anidim naab dimirek dile, fõ bun dile fen, kayau maleg didegneĩd, dogo neid kisi ulum diroukenẽdidig, kayau mosor beberikã anidi, oroya sane fire fire bun waud dalesedig,
\v 7 kayau idi gai toku keleĩ daledig, anĩ ere, momoi anĩ to bagai keleĩdig.
\v 8 Janes Jambres ado Moses kiwai difenen gen, tamo enidig momoi anĩ kiwai difenek, tamo anidi kisi gelele fiya ado, momoiya sã nigin itornẽdin.
\v 9 Anĩ ere, idi gerõ bai to dilauf, ere nigin, tamo uru age difen gen, idi neid kũ fenẽya tamo kayau ganan meleid bun kaisã yaorouf.
\s1 Polem Timoti Ago Dõ Woi Fiyen
\p 
\v 10 Anĩ ere, neu ifelnẽya, neu tobonunã, neu kisi gariya, neu momoiya, sain meluk totol ifareya, wau laa fiya, feseya sã ifareya,
\v 11 kafĩ fiya, darau, naig be fiya Antiok, Ikonium ado, Listra taun bun darau morõ aya alen anĩ ganan õ keleĩ. Anĩ ere, Odug anĩ ganan bun tamal yalelnan.
\v 12 Momoi, tamo kayau ganan, idi Kristus Jesus bun Negur nẽ tobonunã dõ difouf nigin orodiyouf are, idi morõ dalouf.
\v 13 Agef mog, tamo sesen ado idegẽya tamo, sane bunem sane bagai lauf, tunĩ didegneĩd mog, abag didegnẽdiyouf.
\v 14 Anĩ ere, ogo nigin, ereb õ keleĩ wale fen, momoi won anĩ toko tokõ wo ule, ere nigin, idi difelnon are õ idi nigin keleĩ.
\v 15 Agef fen, õ simõ bunem Negur nẽ Itotoya fateul kelein, are õ isennõ di, kisi biya wale fen, Kristus Jesus nigin momoiya bunem, kel yaleyõya kisi feleyauf.
\v 16 Negur nẽ Itotoya ganan are Negur awa uur neseya bunem, are ifelnẽya, sakãya, madur fiya ado, madur ibodõya tai fiya nigin biya.
\v 17 Age fe di, Negur nẽ tamo, kabĩ biya ganan yaleya nigin kisi feleya bagai youf.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Negur ado, Kristus Jesus ĩ isi fen, in tano inouf sain bun, ĩ mata dibodok ado gare den anidi es fediyouf anĩ, idi meleid bun, aya od enei totol bagai arokonok.
\v 2 Biya od wogõ wo; biya od wogõya nigin, sain biya bun ado sain sane bun dodok wo, sain meluk feseya sã ifareya ado faded fiya bunem, madur wo, totol od urokeneĩd, waud walesauf.
\v 3 Sain fau isiyouf bun, tamo biya od nigin to wedereid dinouf. Age fiya ban, idi dogo neid oroya dõ dife fen, wederedim karĩya nigin gegeĩ fedidig anĩ karĩ douf nigin, idegẽya ifelnẽdiya tamo musei gou difediyouf.
\v 4 Idi fau momoi anĩ ditor ken, wedereid fitok du ken, nenerĩ ege anĩ karĩ douf.
\v 5 Anĩ ere, õ ereb ereb ganan bun kisi fokõ wol fen, morõ faali wo, soosi kabĩ wale, ogon kabĩ ganan walel anĩ kisi falauf.
\p 
\v 6 Aya mogo wain sesewi fiya gen fi afalau fenẽ, agef fen, neu ileya sain mogo isil.
\v 7 Aya biya kusĩ aun, aya gudu reya mogo bure afelen, aya momoiya kafĩ afelen.
\v 8 Gama aya nigin, madur bagai nẽ teter dodok fe ibodok, are Odug, Es Fiya Tamo madur bagai, fau naa anĩ bun ifanau fenẽ, anĩ ere, aya dogol sã, idi in isiya tari difef anidig ifenẽdiyouf.
\s1 Pol Timoti Ĩ Gein Kaisã Isiyouf Nigin Irokenen
\p 
\v 9 Aya gein kaisã bagai usiyouf nigin kabĩ totol wale.
\v 10 Ere nigin, Demas ĩ tenebur enei nẽ nigin wau laa fen nigin, itorna fen, Tesalonika taun ilen. Kresen ĩ Galesia provins ilen, age fe di, Taitus ĩ Dalmesia distrik ilen.
\v 11 Luk dogol aya ado mabodok. Mak wale fen, urom usig, ere nigin, ĩ neu kabĩ nigin isennaya kisi feleya.
\v 12 Aya Tikikus Efesus taun sur afen.
\v 13 Õ usiyouf sain bun, neu saket meluk Karpus nẽ fõ bun Troas taun oun atoron anĩ wale urou usiyouf, neu buk kori fediya anĩg urou usiyouf, anĩ atun neu buk kori fediya meme gabar bun itotoya nẽ anĩ to bagai utorõf.
\p 
\v 14 Aleksanda ain kabĩ tamo ĩ, aya gai kiwai totol bagai ifanan. Odug fau ĩ ereb age fen anĩ nigin mala solo sane ifenẽf.
\v 15 Õg ĩ nigin lo welei, ere nigin, ĩ neda od nigin totol bagai kiwai inon.
\p 
\v 16 Aya uruwa kot bun afaren sain, takam to isennan, anĩ ere, ganan ditornan. Anĩ nẽ mala solo to ifenẽdiyouf nigin aya orouf.
\v 17 Anĩ ere, Odug aya sirun ifar fen, megeir ifanan. Age fe di, aya bunem biya od kisi feleya bagai wogõ au di, haiden ganan karĩ douf nigin age fen. Agef fen, aya laion awa bun tamal yalelnan.
\v 18 Odug fau kiwai sane ganan bun tamal yalelna fen, karika bagai in saa tanon irou iseleyauf. Ĩ bun fula fiya medeĩya gai gai ibodkalauf. Momoi.
\s1 Idikeleya Nẽ Aanya
\p 
\v 19 Prisila, Akwila ado, Onesiforus nẽ ibor tar geid, aanya enei wenẽdiyouf.
\v 20 Erastus Korin taun ibodon, agef mog, aya Trofimus dagi mog, Miletus taun oun atornen.
\v 21 Yau sain fau mog, ein kaisã usiyouf nigin kabĩ totol wale. Yubulus, Pudens, Linus, Klodia ado momoiya turã tar ganan aanya sur difonok.
\p 
\v 22 Odug ogon uur ado ibodõf. Wau ifenẽya ã bun ibodõf. 
